reviewText: Came quickly and in perfect condition. I love both movies. Lots of action & suspense.

I love them best I've ever seen them in my life the picture and for John Woo's action blockbuster  and Brain De Palma's suspenseful thriller is great
Thank you so much.

The movies can only be described as full on cheese, but you know what you are getting, so it's hard to complain. The fact that I got them on the cheap side certainly makes them worth picking up for when I feel like throwing something on the tv and checking my brain out at the door.
Excellent double feature. Both films look and sound amazing in Blu-ray.
My wife loved the movie Snake Eyes.  Smartly made.
